{"tid":2500582,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥明詩復出拍亞視網劇 新作由《金枝欲孽》戚其義監製","createTime":"2021-04-22T18:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T01:04:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"27c6a4179c3b7dea73160d2297e1d6d8d9754caf","tid":2500582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:27:16.000Z","msg":"麥明詩在2019年11月時宣布會淡出娛樂圈，之後開始擔任商業顧問工作，不過今日有報導指她將會復出拍劇，但不是拍TVB劇，而是拍亞視網劇，據知這次由亞洲心動娛樂（AMM）香港區副總裁的林文龍出面，向樂小姐借人拍攝，因為是網劇，不是免費頻道，所以和TVB沒有抵觸。<br />\n<br />\n今次麥明詩拍攝的是一套30集網劇，最令人驚喜的是由前TVB神級監製戚其義主理，戚其義以往作品《金枝欲孽》《天與地》等，有收視亦有口碑，自離開TVB後一直都令劇迷期待，他接受訪問時亦表示新作下月開拍，亦表示邀請麥明詩拍劇沒有難度，笑指出錢就可以。而麥明時亦期待今次合作，指自己可用工餘時間拍攝，令她可以保持對戲劇的興趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210423/462071236655058944714928.jpeg/whwGw5w5bgg6zg49Gh5GYpncg9IpeE-JF6YyBRemMgU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210423%2F462071236655058944714928.jpeg%2FwhwGw5w5bgg6zg49Gh5GYpncg9IpeE-JF6YyBRemMgU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=44460755&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb11fbf522834dcc199476ec290dc06741d0797b","tid":2500582,"uid":57911,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:28:21.000Z","msg":"友台返生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f358def3a10d27926c6864bc19020e145b12d3","tid":2500582,"uid":212249,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"條友又話返返去做律師嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f864fc2429563abb019e6e070007ac8f873a5cb5","tid":2500582,"uid":208940,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"做過演員真係返唔到轉頭，任何行業都無娛樂圈咁多姿多彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2bccbdb554f7e59006a49a2ce3ef1fcb7d4bfe","tid":2500582,"uid":3508,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pi